00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:22,160
 That's the first thing.

292
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:23,400
 Here's the second thing.

293
00:12:23,640 --> 00:12:26,960
 I want you to see that three fourths of these,

294
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,600
 three quarters of these

