00:12:36,160 --> 00:12:40,040
 Notice this, escape, insulate and conform

298
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:42,080
 are essentially Christians

299
00:12:42,080 --> 00:12:45,360
 taking what Christ has done in their lives,

