00:12:58,480 --> 00:13:00,920
 It fascinates me that the church through history

307
00:13:00,920 --> 00:13:04,720
 has embraced privatization of faith

308
00:13:04,720 --> 00:13:09,720
 over the engagement of the culture in which it is planted.

309
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:13,040
 And this is significant

