00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,360
 that we see in church history.

312
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,600
 If I'm honest with you,

313
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:21,320
 I think it's something that we all struggle with today.

314
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:24,280
 I think when things get hard,

315
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,960
 when we find things challenging,

316
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,400
 when everybody in our office

317
00:13:27,400 --> 00:13:29,600
 is talking about the craziness of the world,

