 to actually just kind of keep our faith to ourselves

322
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:47,880
 at the very moment when the world needs that faith.

323
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:50,480
 When the world needs that faith the most.

324
00:13:50,480 --> 00:13:53,240
 Think of it this way.

325
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:55,400
 I think one of the greatest temptations

326
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,920
 that we have as the church

327
00:13:56,920 --> 00:13:59,120
 when the world goes crazy is this,

