00:14:50,000 --> 00:14:53,440
 and finding yourself super quiet about it

345
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:57,160
 when you're in a different position or a different community.

346
00:14:57,160 --> 00:14:58,400
 And it's interesting when this happens

