00:14:58,400 --> 00:14:59,960
 because you're probably sitting there thinking like,

348
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,240
 I don't know if I do that, Pastor Andrew.

349
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:02,080
 I don't know if that's for me.

350
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,240
 That's a word for my neighbors

351
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:05,320
 sitting right next to me right now.

352
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:07,800
 Like that's a great word for them, but I think I'm fine.

353
00:15:07,800 --> 00:15:09,080
 I don't think I privatize my faith.

354
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,960
 Do I privatize my faith?

355
00:15:10,960 --> 00:15:12,080
 Let me just be honest.

356
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:14,120
 In a lot of the conversations that I have with us here

