00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,640
 Let me share a few of these.

363
00:15:24,640 --> 00:15:26,280
 Here's the first one.

364
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:28,920
 My faith is just very personal to me.

365
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:32,160
 I hear Christians say this all the time.

366
00:15:32,160 --> 00:15:35,080
 My faith is just really personal to me.

367
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,040
 Oh, it's so personal.

368
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:37,520
 I mean, Christ has saved me

369
00:15:37,520 --> 00:15:40,240
 and he saved me from this terrible time in my life.

370
00:15:40,240 --> 00:15:42,560
 And it's just so deeply personal

371
00:15:42,560 --> 00:15:44,200
 and deeply intimate with him.

372
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:47,360
 And I just am so grateful that I have this private,

373
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:50,080
 personal, intimate relationship with him.

374
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:51,240
 And to be honest with you,

375
00:15:51,240 --> 00:15:53,520
 I'm pretty happy with that relationship.

376
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:56,160
 So happy in fact, that if I shared it

